trans-unit.source: Interacts with the parser to build an <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlSelect"></xref> control.
The <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlSelectBuilder> control interacts with the page parser to build an <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlSelect> control.
Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlSelectBuilder> control to customize the parsing of an <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlSelect> control.
The <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlSelectBuilder.AllowWhitespaceLiterals%2A> property is set to `false` so that white space is always ignored.
Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlSelectBuilder.GetChildControlType%2A> method to determine the type of the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlSelect> control's child controls.
Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlSelectBuilder"></xref> class.
This constructor is used by ASP.NET when parsing the page and creating the control hierarchy.
It is not intended for use in your code.
Determines whether the white space literals in an <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlSelect"></xref> control are to be processed or ignored.

This method overrides the <xref:System.Web.UI.ControlBuilder.AllowWhitespaceLiterals%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method to always ignore white space in the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlSelect> control.
This method always returns `false`, indicating that white space in the <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlSelect"></xref> control is ignored.
Obtains the <xref href="System.Type"></xref> for the <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlSelect"></xref> control's child controls.

Use the <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlSelectBuilder.GetChildControlType%2A> method to return the <xref:System.Type> of a specified child control in an <xref:System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlSelect> control.
The tag name of the child control.
An array of attributes contained in the child control.
The <xref href="System.Type"></xref> of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.HtmlControls.HtmlSelect"></xref> control's specified child control.
